<li>To verify these assumptions , we used GMS assays to show in vitro whether the mutant GcvA proteins could bind to the gcv control region .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=9733689" target="_blank">9733689</a>]<br></li>
