The GcvR protein negatively regulates the gcv operon ( Ghrist & Stauffer , 1995 ) ; its ability to repress is dependent on a functional GcvA protein .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=9611815" target="_blank">9611815</a>]<br></label>
